and supply, commodity, labor and transportation constraints;
•our ability to identify, complete, manage and realize the full extent of the benefits, cost savings or synergies
presented by strategic transactions, including our recently completed acquisitions of Ricolino, Clif Bar, Chipita,
Gourmet Food, Grenade and Hu, and the anticipated closing of our planned divestiture of our developed
