Net Revenues – Net revenues increased $2,139 million (8.0%) to $28,720 million in 2021, and Organic Net Revenue
increased $1,367 million (5.1%) to $27,916 million. Developed markets net revenues increased 6.3% and developed
markets Organic Net Revenue increased 1.6%. Emerging markets net revenues increased 11.4% and emerging
markets Organic Net Revenue increased 12.0%. The underlying changes in net revenues and Organic Net Revenue
are detailed below:
 2021
